ONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">三、校務會議議決事項如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">) </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">校務發展計畫<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>含校園規劃<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">二<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>學校各種重要章則。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">三<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>依法令規定應經校務會議議決之事項。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">四<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>校長交議事項。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">四、校務會議成員比例如下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">未滿二十五班學校由全體教職員工及家長會代表一至五人組織之，家長代表名額由學校定之。二十五班（含）以上由學校決定，比照二十五班以下學校或以代表組織之，如以代表組織，應包含教職員工代表及家長會代表，但教師代表不得少於二分之一，教師代表應經全體教師無記名投票選舉產生，而校務會議組織人數及成員比例由學校定之。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">五、校務會議召開日期：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">應於每學期開學前或開學後七日內及學期結束前十五日內（每學年第一學期期末及第二學期</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">期</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">初之校務會議得合併辦理）由校長召集校務會議成員出席開會，並由校長擔任主席。臨時會由校長召開或經教職員</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">（</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">二十五班</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">（</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">含</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">）</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">以上學校須五分之一以上教職員、未滿二十五班學校須二分之一以上教職員</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">）</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">連署召開。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">六、學校應於開會十日前通知出席人員，並徵詢提案；會議提案應於開會五日前提交校長指定之承辦人員彙整；承辦人員應於開會三日前提供會議資料予出席人員。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">前項期間應扣除星期日及其他休息日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">召開臨時校務會議時，學校最遲應於開會三日前通知出席人員。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">七、校務會議議案之提出依下列規定：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">)</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">校長交議。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>相關之處、室主任提案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">三<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>家長會或教師會提案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">四<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>教職員工及家長經校務會議成員四分之一以上連署之提案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">八、出席人數超過校務會議成員總額二分之一，始能開會。如出席人數未達定額者，校長應宣布於七日內再行召開。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">九、主席應居於公正超然之中立地位，嚴格執行議事規則，維持會議和諧，使會議順利進行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">十、校務會議之程序如下：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">)</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">主席報告出席人數。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">    (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">二<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>主席宣布開會、並確定議程。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">三<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>上次會議決議事項執行情形。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">四<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>校長校務報告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">五<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>各處室工作報告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 6pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-char-indent-count: .5\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">(</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">六<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>提案討論。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">七<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>臨時動議。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">八<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>選舉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     (</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">九<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>散會。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">十一、校長校務報告及</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">各處、</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">室工作報告以書面報告為原則。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">校長校務補充報告以十五分鐘為原則，</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">各處、</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">室補充報告以十分鐘為原則。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">每人針對每一工作報告及提案<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>每一條文<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>發言以兩次為限，每次不超過三分鐘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">十二、議決方式：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">     </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">議案經充分討論後由主席徵詢出席人員有無異議；無異議者，主席應宣布議案通過。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: \"></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: \">議案經充分討論後，有異議者，應提付表決，以出席人員二分之一以上同意後作成決議。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p><p /><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-